ransgender ex-soldier Cho Hyun-ju in season 2 (2024) and season 3 (2025) of Netflix drama Squid Game.","name":"Park Sung-hoon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朴成焄（박성훈），1985年2月18日出生于韩国，毕业于东亚广播艺术大学电影表演系，韩国男演员。","name":"朴成焄","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朴成焄（박성훈，Park Sung-hoon），韓國男演員，名字曾譯朴成勳。2008年在《霜花店：朕的男人》飾演一個小角色正式出道，其後飾演多部戲劇群演配角，一直到2018年透過電視劇《我唯一的守護者》及電影《鬼病院：靈異直播》逐漸提高認知度，同年主演《精神病患者日記》與《出師表》。近期最廣為人知的作品是《黑暗榮耀》及《淚之女王》中的惡角。","name":"朴成焄","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"박성훈","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Пак Сон-хун","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Park Sung-hoon est un acteur sud-coréen. Il a commencé sa carrière d'acteur avec un petit rôle dans le film A Frozen Flower. Il s'est fait connaître grâce aux pièces Rooftop Room Cat, The History Boys et Model Students. Wikipedia","name":"Park Sung-hoon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"樸成焄（박성훈），1985 年 2 月 18 日出生於韓國，畢業於東亞廣播藝術大學電影表演系，韓國男演員。","name":"樸成焄","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_64986_translations":{"at":1772647225432,"data":{"id":64986,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Clare-Hope Ashitey (born February 12, 1987) is an English actress. She attended the Centre Stage School of Performing Arts, Southgate while being educated at The Latymer School, located in the Edmonton area of London, for seven years.\n\nShe took a gap year between school and university to work on the film Children of Men (2006). In 2018, she starred in the Netflix Original crime drama series Seven Seconds.\n\nFrom Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia","name":"Clare-Hope Ashitey","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"克莱尔-霍普·阿什蒂（Clare-Hope Ashitey，1987年2月12日-），英国女演员。她曾就读于索斯盖特的中央舞台表演艺术学校，同时在位于伦敦埃德蒙顿地区的拉蒂默学校接受教育七年。\n\n她花了一年的时间在学校和大学之间拍摄电影《男人的孩子》（2006）。2018年，她出演了Netflix原创犯罪剧集《七秒》。","name":"克莱尔-霍普·阿什蒂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"克萊爾 - 霍普·阿什蒂（Clare - Hope Ashitey，1987 年 2 月 12 日-），英國女演員。她曾就讀於索斯蓋特的中央舞台表演藝術學校，同時在位於倫敦埃德蒙頓地區的拉蒂默學校接受教育七年。\n\n她花了一年的時間在學校和大學之間拍攝電影《男人的孩子》（2006）。2018 年，她出演了 Netflix 原創犯罪劇集《七秒》。","name":"克萊爾 - 霍普·阿什蒂","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Клэр-Хоуп Эшити","primary":false}}]}},"person_1580289_translations":{"at":1772647233542,"data":{"id":1580289,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Cédric Appietto","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_1191274_translations":{"at":1772647233986,"data":{"id":1191274,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US",